videos.description: Temple's Devin Coleman hits the corner 3-pointer with three seconds left to send the Owls into overtime against Tulsa.
videos.headline: Coleman's 3 sends Temple to OT

videos.description: OT (3:35) TEM Quenton DeCosey made Jumper, and-1 opportunity.
videos.headline: Q. DeCosey made Jumper, and-1 opportunity.

videos.description: OT (3:22) TLSA Pat Birt wants to silence the crowd one more time, sinks the Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Shaquille Harrison.
videos.headline: P. Birt wants to silence the crowd one more time, sinks the Three Point Jumper. Assisted by S. Harrison.
